{"tid":1904432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得已經平靜落黎，其實只係你對扭曲社會既妥協","createTime":"2020-02-29T15:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T16:43:13.000Z","uid":81236,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a960524bc9c83e4730d89f22034e41dca6c8864","tid":1904432,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"試問你可唔可以生活係一個充滿警暴既社會？<br />\n<br />\n試問你可唔可以生活係顛倒是非黑白既地方？<br />\n<br />\n試問你可唔可以生活係極權打壓人民為樂既政府？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實以上一直以來都無改變過<br />\n<br />\n如果你已經平靜落黎，改變既係你既心態<br />\n<br />\n一個願意活係扭曲社會而又覺得已經無事發生既心態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係一眾既手足一直以來既堅持<br />\n<br />\n先再次撚起今晚既星火"},{"pid":"edd79e9fca657fbb3dd9b013f80984264fef46af","tid":1904432,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"手足加油<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813233</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"664538bd42e8f364e1229eea43808bf7e7915e28","tid":1904432,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"969bb7ff51c9368d177f7a5698cd8dd851986142","tid":1904432,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57856c98ab80b793a94f23736a62b9e534ebf418","tid":1904432,"uid":244459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67ef34020a8b65a65c9f2ee3eacab0c0a546048c","tid":1904432,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227867d5b00f4296b497c5f73280145d5b59ec17","tid":1904432,"uid":20867,"like":2,"di